{"tid":2260327,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"警員「代表作」 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-10-27T13:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T13:17:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b66be2e9869f7b82e36d3cd618ddf582ddf9f7d9","tid":2260327,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:17:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201027/DKCLCWNUKBAZZNYPTLZ5G7JUSQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201027%2FDKCLCWNUKBAZZNYPTLZ5G7JUSQ%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDAz7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=992eace6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201027%2FDKCLCWNUKBAZZNYPTLZ5G7JUSQ%2F&h=ad5aae58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201027/DKCLCWNUKBAZZNYPTLZ5G7JUSQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警員「代表作」 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fM2bmuYNUUajgZsBpkFtVAuuC80=/801x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MIOXYMPO2JDYVAKSYLUWTA7ZRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfM2bmuYNUUajgZsBpkFtVAuuC80%3D%2F801x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMIOXYMPO2JDYVAKSYLUWTA7ZRU.jpg&h=7ea98de2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旁聽師是抗爭運動衍生的「專業」，旁聽師極需要耐性，當裁判官指庭上作供的警員書面證詞彈出彈入，錯漏百出，仍然要包容，點講好呢？喔，「警員證人並非以寫作為生，所以未能如數家珍道出細節。」法官這樣包庇，旁聽席一地噴飯。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，筆名叫做CYPK的警員（唔使註冊，吹咩），是2025年諾貝爾文學獎頭七名大熱門。<br />\n<br />\n警員不是作家，記者反而似係。「環時」冇證記者付國豪在機場以英語喊打喊揪，法官問是不是撩交打。他辯稱當時只是想表達「無奈、悲傷、諷刺之感。」此乃「真．老作」代表作！叫付國豪大作特作的話，內容包括撞低12歲女童騎在胯下那位阿sir，堪比諷刺性詩人！西灣河交警是在日出前無奈讓悲傷拔槍！作完，你可以打他了。"}]}